      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"benefited the players\"? That's a pretty strong claim. The logs should show if the server actually dropped packets or if it was a local hardware issue. If the frame rate spike caused a discrepancy in hit detection, that's a massive integrity issue for the tournament, not \"drama.\" I need you to be 100% transparent here—if there was a glitch that skewed the outcome, I have to report it to the league. Are you sure you're not just downplaying a legitimate technical failure to keep the report looking clean?",
